race.comment: SCOTT AQUAPHOBIA (1) turned in a plain performance last time when seventh at Horsham over 485m behind Paw Rex (28.17) in a Grade 5. Has ability and looks hard to stop. MCIVOR MORGAN (2) has missed the frame at his last couple but wasn't beaten far three back when third (24.60) at this track in a Special conditions H. Key player on best and worth another try. DESTINI REBEL (3) settled down midfield and held his position to the line when finishing 4th (29.08) at this track. Comes through a solid form race last start. Expected to give a good account. GLOWING ETHICS (8) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.
